==可可采购==

克特多巧克力持续受到了来自全球的道德伦理质疑。数以千计的童工在象牙海岸的可可农场收到的剥削，引起了全球的关注。<ref name="chocolate slavery">{{cite news |author= Humphrey Hawksley |authorlink= Humphrey Hawksley |title= Mali's children in chocolate slavery |publisher= BBC News |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/1272522.stm |date= 12 April 2001 |accessdate= 2 January 2010 |archive-date= 2008-12-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20081226141935/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/1272522.stm |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="accuses companies">{{cite news |author= Humphrey Hawksley |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1311982.stm |title= Ivory Coast accuses chocolate companies |publisher= BBC News |date= 4 May 2001 |accessdate= 4 August 2010 |archive-date= 2009-01-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090114115945/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1311982.stm |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Raghavan1">{{cite web |author= Sudarsan Raghavan and Sumana Chatterjee |title= Slaves feed world's taste for chocolate: Captives common in cocoa farms of Africa |publisher= [[Milwaukee_Journal_Sentinel|Milwaukee Journal Sentinel]] |date= 24 June 2001 |url= http://www2.jsonline.com/news/nat/jun01/slave24r062301.asp |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20060917014323/http://vision.ucsd.edu/~kbranson/stopchocolateslavery/atasteofslavery.html |archivedate= 2006年9月17日 |accessdate= 25 April 2012 |deadurl= yes }}</ref> 
2001年，在卡夫公司上市之后，它与同行业的另几家公司共同签署了{{tsl|en|Harkin-Engel Protocol|哈金·恩格尔协议}}，<ref name="HE Protocol">{{cite web |url= http://www.cocoainitiative.org/images/stories/pdf/harkin%20engel%20protocol.pdf |title= Protocol for the growing and processing of cocoa beans and their derivative products in a manner that complies with ILO Convention 182 concerning the prohibition and immediate action for the elimination of the worst forms of child labor |publisher= International Cocoa Initiative |year= 2001 |accessdate= 25 April 2012 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080724105142/http://www.cocoainitiative.org/images/stories/pdf/harkin%20engel%20protocol.pdf |archivedate= 2008年7月24日 }}</ref>
旨在减少可可豆供应链中的童工数量。

2009年10月，卡夫食品在欧洲上市了第一批带有{{tsl|en|Rainforest Alliance|雨林联盟}}标志的巧克力产品。最早从比利时和法国开始，这些克特多高端黑巧克力至少含有30%以上雨林联盟认证农场生产的可可豆。卡夫食品对外界宣布，他们会逐步将这些认证巧克力推广到英国、德国、西班牙、匈牙利、波兰、葡萄牙、荷兰、加拿大和美国市场。卡夫食品同时计划将雨林联盟认证农场生产的可可豆全线用到其下属的克特多巧克力和马瑞宝巧克力中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rainforest-alliance.org/news.cfm?id=kraft_cocoa |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-11-08 |archive-date=2010-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100710015314/http://www.rainforest-alliance.org/news.cfm?id=kraft_cocoa |dead-url=no }}</ref>

